<br>
Kerafym (the sleeper) is an ancient dragon, and leader of a rebellion within the Draconic race.  There's two big dragon factions, Claws of Veeshan (the Velious dragons), and Ring of Scale (the Kunark Dragons).<br>
<br>
Kerafym was being kept forcefully asleep deep in Sleeper's tomb, a dungeon in the icy wastes of Velious, by four warders, dragons of immense power.<br>
<br>
Annnnnyways, Verant re-vamped Sleeper's tomb this patch.  Some people (/bonk Sirena) started screaming that Kerafym was gone now because the zone was revamped, but it appears possible that he's still there (even amidst the revamp).<br>
<br>
Won't know for sure until a sufficient raid force makes it far enough into the zone to find out.<br>
<br>
